{"word":"ἀδυναμία","slug":"ἀδυναμία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀδυναμία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δύναμις'><el>δύναμις</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>want of strength</i> or <i>power, inability, incapacity</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>ἀδ. τοῦ ἀδικεῖν</el> <i>for</i> wrong-doing, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>poverty</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}